data.description: PRICE REDUCTION! This single story home is located in a quiet neighborhood of Lancaster. With 1,700 square feet of living space this home includes four bedrooms and two bathrooms, newer wood like flooring, fresh paint and an open floor plan. Upon entering, you are greeted with a formal living room and dining room. A pocket door separates the dining room and kitchen. The kitchen opens up to a warm family room with a cozy fire place. Down the hall you'll find the master bedroom & master bath along with a huge walk-in closet. There is a guest bath with double sinks and a tub & shower combo. There are three additional generous sized bedrooms. One bedroom includes a walk in closet. Off the kitchen is a a bright sunroom that opens up to the back yard which is perfect for entertaining! The patio has plenty of space for furniture and a buit-in bar-b-que and bar for outdoor dining. The custom  pool has a beautiful water feature and will be the center of fun for your family and friend's gatherings! Solar is included!
